            "id": 6007846,
            "title": "華航攜手台積電首創商務旅行SAF減碳 估年減逾千噸碳排",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>華航 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2610:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2610\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2610-TW</a>) 今 (5) 日宣布與台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 合作，推動「企業商務旅行 SAF 減碳計畫」，為國內首創航空公司結合企業差旅使用台灣自產永續航空燃油 (Sustainable Aviation Fuels, SAF) 並運用碳抵換機制，預估全年台積電員工差旅可減少逾千噸碳排。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007846%2Fl%2F40cffea0a7855a22d7565d362abb4332.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007846%2Fl%2F40cffea0a7855a22d7565d362abb4332.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007846%2Fl%2F40cffea0a7855a22d7565d362abb4332.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007846%2Fl%2F40cffea0a7855a22d7565d362abb4332.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007846%2Fl%2F40cffea0a7855a22d7565d362abb4332.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007846%2Fl%2F40cffea0a7855a22d7565d362abb4332.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007846%2Fl%2F40cffea0a7855a22d7565d362abb4332.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007846%2Fl%2F40cffea0a7855a22d7565d362abb4332.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007846%2Fl%2F40cffea0a7855a22d7565d362abb4332.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007846%2Fl%2F40cffea0a7855a22d7565d362abb4332.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007846%2Fl%2F40cffea0a7855a22d7565d362abb4332.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007846%2Fl%2F40cffea0a7855a22d7565d362abb4332.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007846%2Fl%2F40cffea0a7855a22d7565d362abb4332.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007846%2Fl%2F40cffea0a7855a22d7565d362abb4332.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007846%2Fl%2F40cffea0a7855a22d7565d362abb4332.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007846%2Fl%2F40cffea0a7855a22d7565d362abb4332.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007846%2Fl%2F40cffea0a7855a22d7565d362abb4332.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">華航攜手台積電首創商務旅行SAF減碳。(圖：華航提供)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>華航今年擴大向國內油商採購在台自產的 SAF 添加於桃園出發國際航班，可較傳統燃油減少超過 80% 的碳排，並持續拓展 「SAF 夥伴合作計畫」，邀集上下游廠商和客戶共同參與。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>華航表示，台積電是全球半導體產業巨擘，也是重要企業客戶之一，藉由本次的商務旅行減碳合作，樹立永續共好標竿，開創台灣 SAF 發展新里程。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>隨著台積電布局全球，員工商務旅行需求強勁，華航估，雙方減碳合作後全年差旅可減少逾千噸碳排。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台積電表示，員工商旅橫跨全球，華航不僅提供飛行的優質服務，也是台灣業界推動 SAF 的先驅，雙方共同推動跨產業的永續行動，支持價值鏈能源轉型，意義非凡。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>華航長期推動永續發展，為國內首家於 2017 年起新機飛渡導入使用 SAF 的航空公司，也是首個於商用載客航班添加 SAF 的國籍航空。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
